<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>NKSBOT — Connexion</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{background:#08080f;color:#f1f0ff;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden}
.bg{position:fixed;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%,rgba(124,58,237,0.15) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
.card{background:rgba(13,13,26,0.95);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.25);border-radius:24px;padding:3rem 2.5rem;text-align:center;max-width:420px;width:90%;position:relative;z-index:1;backdrop-filter:blur(20px)}
.logo{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:800;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff,#a855f7);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;margin-bottom:.4rem}
.version{display:inline-block;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.2);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.4);color:#a855f7;padding:.2rem .8rem;border-radius:20px;font-size:.75rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.sub{color:#8b87b0;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;line-height:1.6}
.btn{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:.8rem;background:#5865F2;color:white;padding:1rem 2rem;border-radius:12px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(88,101,242,0.3)}
.btn:hover{background:#4752C4;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 0 50px rgba(88,101,242,0.5)}
.btn svg{width:22px;height:22px}
.note{margin-top:1.5rem;color:#6b6890;font-size:.8rem}
.features{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:.6rem;margin-bottom:2rem;text-align:left}
.feature{background:rgba(124,58,237,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.15);border-radius:8px;padding:.6rem .8rem;font-size:.8rem;color:#8b87b0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg"></div>
<div class="card">
  <div class="logo">NKSBOT</div>
  <div class="version">v1.01 — MAJ disponible</div>
  <p class="sub">Configure ton serveur Discord<br>depuis ce panel</p>
  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature">⚙️ Config complète</div>
    <div class="feature">🤖 IA intégrée</div>
    <div class="feature">🔔 Notifications</div>
    <div class="feature">🎫 Tickets avancés</div>
  </div>
  <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03z"/></svg>
    Connexion avec Discord
  </a>
  <p class="note">🔒 Seules les permissions nécessaires sont demandées</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
